Scrum master must ensure:
1. PO availibility to answer queries on user stories
2. teams speak up and ask questions on user stories to brin clarity
3. if possible do they, user story workshop along with PO and Team

Development Team
a. if writing or reviewing user stories, adhere to INVEST principles
b. ask questions to get clarity on user stories
c. ensure that the acceptance criteria are written well and is complete
d. allow conversation to happen with team and PO on user stories to get clarity
e. write user stories from business user perspective and NOT from technicall perspective
